com.ojcoleman.europa.configurable

Annotation Type Prototype


  • @Documented
@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Prototype
    For fields in sub-classes of ConfigurableBase, this annotation indicates that the field is for a user configurable PrototypeBase object, e.g. via a JSON configuration file. The field must be of a type that extends PrototypeBase. See ConfigurableBase and PrototypeBase for more information.
    Author:
    O. J. Coleman
    See Also:
    Configurable, Parameter, Component
